text: So my industrial revolution take is valid.
Watching the CZ review show I realize I misread [[Goblin Engineer]] - I thought it said you could only bring back an artifact that cost 3 less than the one you sacrifice vs. one for 3 CMC or less.

When Goblin Engineer enters the battlefield, you may search your library for an artifact card, put it into your graveyard, then shuffle your library.
